title: 407: No Such Thing As An Echidna With An After Eight Mint
content: Happy New Year! It's the Fish Live Compilation Special! Dan, James, Anna and Andrew show why they're absolute pro podcasters, with a new bunch of outtakes and near disasters from our live shows.
